summary: A cabin outside of Whiterun, near Chillfurrow farm.
descriptionHtml:
A cabin outside of Whiterun, near Chillfurrow farm. Includes a dungeon-like area attached to the basement which I plan on expanding upon soon.
<br />
<br />**PLEASE NOTE: This is my first mod. I have little idea on how to fully use the Creation Kit. Criticism is appreciated, honestly.** 
<br />
<br />For a fast way into the cabin just type coc WhiterunCreekCabin in command. 
<br />
<br />This is a work in progress, you will come across a spot in the dungeon where it just stops. I just want opinions on what Im doing wrong so its not as hard to fix in the future. 
<br />
<br />Installation should be straightforward, just drag and drop in data folder.
<br />
<br />PS: One of my biggest concerns is how to rename a door so that it actually says Whiterun Creek Cabin instead of just Storage Marker. Help would be appreciated.
author: ryanmeyer370
